      "text": "橋本さんの提案で、星見プロからみんなに\n誕生日プレゼントとして慰安旅行を計画したんだ",
      "startTime": 4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_52_01_short/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_02_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "旅行先は俺の方で考えようと思っているけれど\nもし、希望があったら受け付けるよ",
      "startTime": 11.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_52_01_short/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_02_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "グループは誕生日が近い人達で組ませてもらったが……\n日頃の疲れを存分に癒して来てくれ！",
      "startTime": 17.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_52_01_short/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_02_01-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "ええっ……！\nええっ……！",
      "startTime": 19.9333347321,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_52_01_short/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_02_01-kan001.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……？",
      "startTime": 22.1466686138,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_52_01_short/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_02_01-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "やったーー！",
      "startTime": 23.4333364805,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_52_01_short/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_02_01-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "おお～",
      "startTime": 25.5333382926,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――星見プロ誕生日慰安旅行in北海道",
      "startTime": 28.3066717531,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkatown-00-noon.webp",
