    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_52_01_short/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_02_01-kan002.m4a",
      "text": "さっむ、うっざ！　おい{user}！\nいつまでkanaを待たせる訳！？",
      "startTime": 35.0666670482,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkatown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkatown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 37.7436369143
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_52_01_short/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_02_01-kan003.m4a",
      "text": "早くタクシー拾って来いよ！\n……ったく、これで旅館ボロかったら許さないから！",
      "startTime": 40.582566341,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkatown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkatown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 44.9400324706
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_52_01_short/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_02_01-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "うう……さとみさんがもう暖かいから薄着で\n大丈夫かもって言ってたけど……意外と寒いです！",
      "startTime": 49.6158999287,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kan_52_01_short/sud_vo_adv_event_2502_02_01-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "そうね……私も沙季の言う通り上着でも\n持って来れば良かったわ……",
      "startTime": 59.5666673025,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hokkatown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hokkatown-00-noon",
